                                                mv<ex>n</ex> aldre skyrd oll j fiolnes
                                            fei<ex>n</ex>gi stilis hond m<ex>ed</ex> stal
                                                <ex>ok</ex> rond stoltare gvllit h</q>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>En mand og kone ønsker hinanden held og lykke: <q
                                            xml:lang="is">Gud v<ex>er</ex>e m<ex>ed</ex> ydur
                                                bo<ex>n</ex>de min <ex>ok</ex> gefi yd<ex>ur</ex>
                                            lif <ex>ok</ex> lucku</q> and <q xml:lang="is"> Gvd
